<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>الكُست؛<span class="c5"> يَعْنِي:</span> القُسط: قَالَهُ الشَّيْخُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>